## Quick Start

### 1) Backend

```bash
cd backend
cp .env.example .env
uv sync
uv run alembic upgrade head
uv run uvicorn main:app --reload --port {{ backend_port }}
```

### 2) Frontend

```bash
cd ../frontend
cp .env.example .env
npm install
npm run dev -- --port {{ frontend_port }}
```

